<pre><code>private static final String TEXT = "this a test 1: $\\$$,test 2: $\\underline{\\rm defund}$, test 3:$$\\underline{\\rm defund}$$"; </code></pre>  <p>Others told me a python pattern:</p>  <pre><code>re.compile(r'(?=([^\\]?))(?:(?P&lt;bound2&gt;\$\$)|\$)(.*?[^\\])(?:(?(bound2)\$\$|\$))', re.S) </code></pre>  <p>Expected: </p>  <pre><code>$\$$ or \$, $\underline{\rm defund}$ or \underline{\rm defund} </code></pre>  <p>But I use it in android,Java doesn't support <code>express pattern</code>.Who can write a <code>Java Pattern</code> for me or give me some tips?</p>